       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. BooleanTester.

       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.

       88 My88Level VALUE 99.

       01 MyGroup.
        05 MySecondLevel.
            10 levelBool TYPE BOOL.

       01 Var1 pic X.
       01 Var2 TYPE BOOL.
       01 Var3 TYPE BOOL.
       01 Var4 pic 9.

       01 myBool TYPE BOOL.
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       MOVE My88Level TO My88Level.
       MOVE myBool TO myBool. 
       MOVE MyGroup::levelBool TO myBool. 
       IF myBool = myBool
         continue
       END-IF.
       SET myBool TO TRUE.
       SET myBool TO FALSE.

        EVALUATE TRUE
         WHEN myBool CONTINUE
        END-EVALUATE

          display var2 "rtzerz" var3 "zerzerze"
             'zrzr' var2
      
           string var2 var3 Var4
                delimited by size
                into Var1
           end-string
      
           evaluate var2
              when var2
                  continue
              when var3
                 continue
              when Var1 = '99998'
                 continue
              when other
                 continue
           end-evaluate
           .
       END PROGRAM BooleanTester.